{"tid":1040188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「抖音」美國涉非法收集兒童資料　罰款4400萬","createTime":"2019-02-28T02:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T01:54:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8b19165a76c7fcd3c825c7d159206c3b57265e20","tid":1040188,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190228/s00005/ef7df887bb6ee1bc79a6e5f98bb71b30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190228%2Fs00005%2Fef7df887bb6ee1bc79a6e5f98bb71b30.jpg&h=d66d27ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影音分享平台「抖音」在美國涉嫌非法收集兒童個人資料，在當地時間周三（27日）被罰款570萬美元（約4400萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦貿易委員會（FTC）人員表示，海外版「抖音」（<a href=\"http://昔日為Musical.ly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%98%94%E6%97%A5%E7%82%BAMusical.ly&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td3obfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=2203b20d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">昔日為Musical.ly</a>）在未有就13歲以下用家向其家長或監護人取得同意確認下，收集用家姓名、電郵地址及其他個人資料，違反當地的兒童網上私隱保護法。FTC指出，「抖音」的判罰是至今就涉及兒童私隱調查中，罰款最高的一次。<br />\n<br />\n「抖音」發表聲明表示，會以用家安全及良好體驗為首要考慮，會加強保障用戶私隱，包括加入讓家長進一步保障子女私隱的設定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190228/s00005/1551314265787/「抖音」美國涉非法收集兒童資料-罰款4400萬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190228%2Fs00005%2F1551314265787%2F%E3%80%8C%E6%8A%96%E9%9F%B3%E3%80%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE4400%E8%90%AC&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td3obfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=98c65fdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190228%2Fs00005%2F1551314265787%2F%E3%80%8C%E6%8A%96%E9%9F%B3%E3%80%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE4400%E8%90%AC&h=cc3d4afc\" target=\"_blank\">